Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.36,0:00:20.77,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:23.07,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.07,0:00:29.89,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.20,0:00:40.51,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.51,0:00:43.98,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:49.52,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between\Nthe sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.52,0:00:55.74,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:01:02.75,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good\Ntime just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:07.08,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:09.34,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:16.28,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.49,0:01:26.98,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:30.23,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:35.78,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.09,0:01:41.99,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing,\Nlet's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:49.04,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave\Nthe rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:53.53,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.53,0:01:55.74,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.74,0:02:00.08,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.08,0:02:02.85,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:04.87,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.87,0:02:06.62,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.62,0:02:08.19,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:09.85,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:11.47,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.47,0:02:12.98,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:14.64,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.64,0:02:15.71,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:19.91,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:22.20,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:26.65,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.65,0:02:29.00,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:33.19,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.19,0:02:35.54,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.54,0:02:39.51,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:42.67,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.65,0:03:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become \Nthe next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and \Nless able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.30,0:03:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leaving the female-only island of Amazon Lily
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to rescue his brother Ace who \Nis waiting to be executed,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy stowed away on a navy ship with \Nthe Pirate Empress Boa Hancock's help
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.04,0:03:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and headed to the Great Prison - Impel Down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, the rest of the Straw Hat crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who had been ejected from the Sabaody \NArchipelago by Bartholomew Kuma are...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.40,0:04:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Friends' Whereabouts! Bridging \Nthe Islands and Vicious Vegetations!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love-Love Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we gonna survive this trip?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll never learn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, the food is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, haven't we reached Ace yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm afraid it'll take more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.89,0:04:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Yum-yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.64,0:04:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:04:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-All right, I'll make some.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,tell me about your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I mean, it's no big deal! \NI'm just making conversation!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I want to know more \Nabout you or something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, which one of them should I start with?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.56,0:05:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro, Sanji, Usopp, Brook, \NFranky, Nami, Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami? Robin?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are girls?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You're spilling the tea water.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but I can't be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! Why, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.12,0:05:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.31,0:05:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I won't back off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.44,0:05:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a person!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen clothes like these...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's from somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.98,0:06:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.04,0:06:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.80,0:06:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in Tequila Wolf, a \Ncountry in the East Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you cold? Do you want \Nto come to our house?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it won't put you out, \Nyes, I would like to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.55,0:06:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hustle up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.89,0:07:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soran! Did you go out without asking again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that! You hid \Nfrom the officers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like she's from somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was lying down in this snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A drifter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.41,0:07:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe, a wanted person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, she wouldn't come to the \Nplace like this if she were sane.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.04,0:07:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I'm not welcomed here. I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.34,0:07:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll look after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you do if the officers find \Nout that we're giving a stranger shelter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.85,0:07:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd take all the responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.39,0:08:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.22,0:08:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you gonna hide her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the loft?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.85,0:08:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay for a while there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you people serious? Shouldn't \Nwe turn her in before it's too late?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late. She's already in our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna regret it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.37,0:08:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep me out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get any ideas. She has to \Nleave as soon as her wounds heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.42,0:08:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she gets well, there's \Nnothing for her in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.64,0:08:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.90,0:08:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.65,0:08:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.84,0:08:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something smells so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.90,0:08:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't use any perfume.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.69,0:08:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe, that's the scent of the outside world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't left this country since I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.24,0:09:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a traveler? Did you \Ncome from a hot climate?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.86,0:09:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I've been traveling \Naround on a ship but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.94,0:09:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a big ship? What kind \Nof island did you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.40,0:09:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen any beautiful \Nflowers or birds? And...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.44,0:09:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soran! The break is over! \NHurry and get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.99,0:09:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You work this late at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We work all day and night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.23,0:09:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me about the outside world later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'll be waiting for you, Soran.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.04,0:10:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that I can make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.69,0:10:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, did I wake you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.04,0:10:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soran, you're so dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.27,0:10:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of work do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We are making a bridge.\N--A bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This country is on a bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.53,0:11:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bridge will connect \Nmany islands together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This construction has been \Ngoing on for centuries now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.28,0:11:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what the officers say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For centuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me. Where are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.08,0:11:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm from...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My home island no longer exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.16,0:11:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I traveled many islands and oceans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.04,0:11:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soran?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.01,0:11:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're these?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.28,0:11:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're drawings of islands \Nall throughout the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.40,0:11:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never left this place so I \Ndrew them out of my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.03,0:11:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I draw an island, it makes \Nme feel like I'm visiting that island
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.37,0:11:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I can forget how difficult life is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.17,0:11:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Sky Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does the island in the sky really exist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:12:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes.\N--Tell me about your trip there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.86,0:12:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... where should I start?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.93,0:12:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like the outside world \Nis as much fun as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every day they push us around and \Nwork us until we're exhausted but
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.40,0:12:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when I think about it, maybe \Nmaking a bridge isn't so bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.04,0:12:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it links to a distant island someday,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,anyone can travel freely \Nby crossing the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll travel all over the world
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and draw pictures of actual islands!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.72,0:12:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a great dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.15,0:13:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! So, tell me more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.58,0:13:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we join?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The woman is in the loft.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.07,0:13:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't forget your promise \Nto get me out of this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don't move!\N--W-What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Outta my way!\N--We're looking for the stranger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you resist us, we'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody must've told the \Nofficers! They're here for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you're hiding a \Nsuspicious woman in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.48,0:14:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These days, people opposed to the \Nconstruction of the bridge threaten the order.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.04,0:14:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn her over!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know a woman like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use searching here! \NWe're tired so leave us alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Auntie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.29,0:14:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't cooperate, we have to arrest \Nall of you and question you one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what we do to get the \Ninformation we want, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, I found these!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this crap?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.64,0:15:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Islands?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.94,0:15:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I drew them! Give them back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.43,0:15:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You drew islands?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amusing! How silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give them back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.53,0:15:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me where the woman is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NThen you'll get your drawings back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.49,0:15:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.17,0:15:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once again, where's the woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.03,0:15:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you cooperate, we'll get \Nyou out of here someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.81,0:15:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you can see the outside world for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One last chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the woman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You people won't leave this place \Nfor the rest of your life anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.95,0:16:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take all of them in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.20,0:16:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna torture them until they speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.24,0:16:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And show no mercy to the kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.63,0:16:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.67,0:16:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clutch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:16:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.52,0:17:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stay away! P-Put your hands up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry! Forgive me! \NPlease don't hurt me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.81,0:17:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.64,0:17:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's her! I got her cornered!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.79,0:17:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Someone! I need backup!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.67,0:17:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing? Didn't you hear him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.58,0:17:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she the one that you're looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.26,0:17:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go and get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.43,0:17:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not welcome here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.72,0:17:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?! Go and cover him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.48,0:17:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.85,0:17:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you get away for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:17:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't forget your rebellious behavior!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.74,0:18:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.33,0:18:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a country of laborers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.16,0:18:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull! Pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.91,0:18:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people who work here are \Ncriminals from various countries
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.37,0:18:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or citizens of countries that refused \Nto be allied with the World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.66,0:18:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On your feet! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.18,0:18:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other word, slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:18:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long until the bridge is complete?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.00,0:19:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.88,0:19:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been under construction for 700 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,700 years? For what purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.01,0:19:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.88,0:19:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll become one of laborers,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so all you have to worry about \Nis making the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.34,0:19:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This islands look like a flower blooming \Nin the ocean. It's called Bowin Islands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.76,0:19:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go Usopp Exploring Party!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I'm the leader! \NUsopp the king of snipers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here is my crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They couldn't be here due \Nto unforeseen circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.71,0:19:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder whether Luffy and others are alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.64,0:19:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't do anything without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that they're crying for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.78,0:19:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta hurry to save them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.78,0:20:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, just the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew of Usopp Exploring Party \Nshould always be on the lookout!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.99,0:20:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I get off this island? And...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Is anybody here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.41,0:20:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me this is a deserted island!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! It's the My-Heart-Will-Stop-Beating- \NIf-I-Don't-See-Anybody Syndrome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Collapse!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.28,0:20:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Isn't anybody here for real?! \NStop being shy and come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.39,0:20:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, there you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.38,0:21:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be doing a little well!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.05,0:21:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Are you gonna eat that'n?\N--Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.05,0:21:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you saved me! Thanks, \NMr. Whoever-you-are!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.61,0:21:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Heracles'n!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.38,0:22:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! That's a cool name!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.13,0:22:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You think so'n?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.88,0:22:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Usopp! Nice meetin' you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.57,0:22:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this good to eat? I've \Nnever seen a fruit like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.89,0:22:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine'n! Usopp'n!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.06,0:22:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my name is Heracles'n!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.07,0:22:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, OK, fine - that's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.20,0:22:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure smells delicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.25,0:22:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just lick it and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.87,0:22:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp'n!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.48,0:22:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy! What was it?! Did \Nthat plant try to eat me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.06,0:22:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, they're man-eating plants'n!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.39,0:22:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man-eating?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.92,0:23:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell am I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.16,0:23:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Swindling Forest - Glinston!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.47,0:23:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-H-Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.24,0:23:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my name is Hera...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.40,0:23:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro arrives at an old castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.32,0:23:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where he runs into Perona.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.75,0:23:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro wants to return to his friends, \Nbut for some reason, Perona stops him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.13,0:23:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Around that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.96,0:23:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook is being hailed as \NSatan, the king of demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.85,0:23:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.19,0:23:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Friends' Whereabouts! A Princess \NNegativity and the King of Demons!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.04,0:23:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
